Have a great day!")"},"id":"8ccabdeab89142f0a043008ae64073db","name":"End"},{"type":"ScriptedAction","script":"(function execute() {
 var gr = new GlideRecordSecure('incident');
 gr.addQuery('assigned_to', vaInputs.user);
 gr.addQuery('state', '!=', vaVars.resolved_state)
 gr.addActiveQuery();
 gr.orderByDesc('sys_updated_on');

 var start = parseInt(vaVars.index);
 var end = start + parseInt(vaVars.limit);
 gr.chooseWindow(start, end, true);
 gr.query();

 vaVars.count = gr.getRowCount();
 var results = [];
 while(gr.next()) {
 results.push({

 });
 }

 vaVars.results = JSON.stringify(results);
})()

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.cmcTools</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>cmcTools</name><script><![CDATA[var cmcTools = Class.create();
cmcTools.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {
    },

	sendMessage: function() {
	try { 
		 var r = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('CoinMarketCap', 'GET');
			 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('limit', gs.getProperty("hml.cmc.max.records"));
			 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('endpoint', gs.getProperty("hml.cmc.endpoint"));
			 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('start', '1');
			 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('sort', 'market_cap');
			 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('key', gs.getProperty("hml.cmc.token"));
			 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('convert', 'USD');
			 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('invocation', 'cryptocurrency/listings/latest');

			 var response = r.execute();
			 var requestBody = r.getRequestBody();
			 var responseBody = response.getBody();
			 var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
			gs.print(requestBody);
			gs.print(responseBody);
			gs.print(httpStatus);
		return JSON.parse(responseBody);
			}
			catch(ex) {
			 var message = ex.message;
		}
	},
	
	sendOtherCoinsMessage: function() {
	try { 

	var r = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('CoinMarketCap', 'GETSpecific');
	r.setStringParameterNoEscape('endpoint', gs.getProperty("hml.cmc.endpoint"));
	r.setStringParameterNoEscape('coins', gs.getProperty("hml.cmc.otherCoins"));
	r.setStringParameterNoEscape('key', gs.getProperty("hml.cmc.token"));
	r.setStringParameterNoEscape('invocation', 'cryptocurrency/quotes/latest?symbol=');

	var response = r.execute();
	var requestBody = r.getRequestBody();
	var responseBody = response.getBody();
	var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
	return JSON.parse(responseBody);
			}
			catch(ex) {
			 var message = ex.message;
		}
	},
	
    type: 'cmcTools'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>jaskidd05</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-08 16:03:53</sys_created_on><sys_id>f1da4771dbc033001c7e9c68db961923</sys_id><sys_mod_count>13</sys_mod_count><sys_name>cmcTools</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_f1da4771dbc033001c7e9c68db961923</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>jaskidd05</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-18 14:18:18</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

Have a great day!"},"id":"a022f8faf03f451d85d07b920b5230d5","name":"End"},{"type":"ScriptedAction","script":"(function execute() {
 /*
 Determining whether there are,
 1. Active incidents opened by the current user

 */

 incidents.addQuery('active', true);

 incidents.query();

 reqItems.query();

 reqItemsCount = reqItems.getAggregate('COUNT');

 vaVars.requested_item_count = reqItemsCount;
})()

"},"optional":false,"expression_mode":"script","script":"(function execute() {
 /*
 1. Query the requested items table and get all the active items requested_for the user
 2. Show the recently updated 5(limit) requested items, apply pagination if there are more than 5.
 */

 var index = parseInt(vaVars.index);
 var limit = parseInt(vaVars.limit);
 var count = 0;

 var options = []; 
 var gr = new GlideRecord(vaVars.table_name);
 gr.addActiveQuery();
 if (vaVars.table_name == 'incident')
 gr.addQuery('caller_id', vaInputs.user);
 else 
 gr.addQuery('request.requested_for', vaInputs.user);

 gr.orderByDesc('sys_updated_on');
 gr.chooseWindow(index, index + limit, true);
 gr.query();

 count = gr.getRowCount();
 vaVars.count = count;
 var cnt = 0;

 while(gr.next()) {
 if (gr.canRead()) {
 if (vaVars.table_name == 'incident')
 options.push({ 'value': gr.getUniqueValue(), 'label': gr.getDisplayValue('short_description') + ' [' + gr.getValue('number') + ']'});
 else
 options.push({ 'value': gr.getUniqueValue(), 'label': gr.getDisplayValue('cat_item') + ' [' + gr.getValue('number') + ']'});
 cnt++;
 } 
 }

 if ( index > 0 && cnt > 0 )
 options.push({ 'value': 'prev', 'label': gs.getMessage('Show previous')});
 if ( count > index + limit )
 options.push({ 'value': 'more', 'label': gs.getMessage('Show more')});
 
 return options;

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_cb_design_topic"><sys_cb_design_topic action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><compiled_topic display_value="Check IT Ticket Status">b6b7ecb5db1433001c7e9c68db9619d1</compiled_topic><design_definition>{"type":"FlowTopic","triggers":[{"type":"Trigger","name":"c94fd4c6ece649e1a5bc517d3d4dbcfe","triggerType":"request","id":"c94fd4c6ece649e1a5bc517d3d4dbcfe"}],"goals":[{"name":"Conversation flow for checking status.","trigger_id":"c94fd4c6ece649e1a5bc517d3d4dbcfe","nodes":[{"type":"StartGoal","goal_id":"3fc1d64b955149d69c86685e542f693f","greeting_msg":{"type":"String","mode":"string","value":""},"id":"14c4bc9ca7ef4acb9e50a2a88fd14c45","name":"Start"},{"type":"TerminateGoal","goal_id":"3fc1d64b955149d69c86685e542f693f","confirmation_msg":{"type":"String","mode":"string","value":"gs.getMessage("Thanks for using our support chat! Have a great day!")"},"id":"a022f8faf03f451d85d07b920b5230d5","name":"End"},{"type":"ScriptedAction","script":"(function execute() {
 /*
 Determining whether there are,
 1. Active incidents opened by the current user
 2. Active Requested items requested for the current user
 and assigning the corresponding script variables.
 */
